OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777392671
OL,3,CTaylor Swift terror suspect pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to Vienna concert plot
OL,6,FA man accused of planning a terror
OL,7,Fattack at a Taylor Swift concert in
OL,8,FVienna nearly two years ago has
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to charges relating to
OL,10,Fthe plot.
OL,12,FThe Austrian citizen, 21, known only
OL,13,Fas Beran A. in line with Austrian
OL,14,Fprivacy rules, began his trial on
OL,15,FTuesday in connection with the concert
OL,16,Fplot, as well as other offences in the
OL,17,FUnited Arab Emirates and Saudi Arabia.
OL,19,FAustrian media reports that he pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to all the charges relating
OL,21,Fspecifically to the concert attack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
