OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777392671
OL,3,CTaylor Swift terror suspect pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to Vienna concert plot
OL,6,FBeran A. was accused of planning to
OL,7,Ftarget crowds around the Ernst Happel
OL,8,FStadium with knives or explosives in
OL,9,FAugust 2024, and pledging allegiance
OL,10,Fto the Islamic State group.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHe was arrested on August 7, 2024 - a
OL,18,Fday before Swift was due to perform
OL,19,Fthe first of her three sold-out
OL,20,Fperformances in the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
