PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777392671
OL,3,CTaylor Swift terror suspect pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to Vienna concert plot
OL,6,FHis arrest came after a tip-off from
OL,7,Fthe CIA and prompted the singer to
OL,8,Fcancel her shows.
OL,10,FThe Ernst Happel Stadium had been due
OL,11,Fto hold 65,000 people during each
OL,12,Fnight's shows, with another 30,000
OL,13,Feach night expected to show up outside
OL,14,Fthe venue.
OL,16,FBeran A. had hoped to "kill as many
OL,17,Fpeople as possible" in the planned
OL,18,Fattack, authorities said in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
