PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777392671
OL,3,CTaylor Swift terror suspect pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to Vienna concert plot
OL,6,FHe was also accused of networking with
OL,7,Fother members of the Islamic State
OL,8,Fgroup ahead of the attack to discuss
OL,9,Fthe purchase of weapons, seeking to
OL,10,Fillegally buy weapons, and swearing
OL,11,Fallegiance to the militant group.
OL,13,FAuthorities searched his apartment the
OL,14,Fday he was arrested and found bomb-
OL,15,Fmaking materials.
OL,17,F"Having our Vienna shows cancelled was
OL,18,Fdevastating," Swift wrote in a
OL,19,Fstatement posted to Instagram two
OL,20,Fweeks after she cancelled the shows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
