PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777392671
OL,3,CTaylor Swift terror suspect pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to Vienna concert plot
OL,6,F"The reason for the cancellations
OL,7,Ffilled me with a new sense of fear,
OL,8,Fand a tremendous amount of guilt
OL,9,Fbecause so many people had planned on
OL,10,Fcoming to those shows."
OL,12,FBeran A., alongside two other men, is
OL,13,Falso accused of planning to carry out
OL,14,Fsimultaneous attacks in Saudi Arabia,
OL,15,FTurkey, and the UAE in the name of the
OL,16,FIslamic State group, months before the
OL,17,FSwift concert.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
