PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777392671
OL,3,CTaylor Swift terror suspect pleads
OL,4,Cguilty to Vienna concert plot
OL,6,FThe 21-year-old pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Ftraveling to Dubai with terrorist
OL,8,Fintent, but has pleaded not guilty to
OL,9,Fthe accessory of attempted murder in
OL,10,FMecca, Austrian newspaper Kurier
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FThe other men were not involved in the
OL,14,Fplot to attack the Swift venue.
OL,16,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,17,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,18,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,19,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
